sentences: Carlos Roberto PenaVega (né Pena Jr.; born August 15, 1989) is an American actor and singer.

In August 2013, PenaVega became engaged to actress Alexa Vega after meeting at Bible study.
The couple married on January 4, 2014, in Puerto Vallarta, Mexico, both taking PenaVega as their married name.
The couple's first son, Ocean King PenaVega, was born on December 7, 2016.
